Changelog
=========

0.3.2 (October 10th, 2019)
--------------------------

* Fixed: Django version in package requirements

0.3.0 (October 10th, 2019)
--------------------------

* New: Added compatibility with python 3.6 and Django 2.x.

0.2.5 (September 26th, 2018)
--------------------------

* Updated: Bundling `html` library to avoid installation issues with newer Python/Setuptools versions

0.2.4 (May 15th, 2018)
--------------------------

* Updated: Improved handling of missing files

0.2.0 (May 8th, 2018)
--------------------------

* New: Refactored file/path handling and added `includegeneric` template tag

0.1.0 (July 28th, 2016)
--------------------------

* New: Initial version supporting basic CSS and JS inlining from static files
